1
00:00:13,416 --> 00:00:18,240
(Bench Part)

2
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:27,920
(My name is Chun Peilan.)

3
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:31,399
(Can you believe that I,
who am currently making rose pastries,)

4
00:00:31,839 --> 00:00:33,640
(am experiencing
the biggest change in my life?)

5
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:37,799
(Chun Peilan, 28, thrifty, but with bad luck)
(On my 10th birthday, Mother took me to the temple.)

6
00:00:38,399 --> 00:00:40,039
(I prayed to God in my heart)

7
00:00:40,359 --> 00:00:42,640
(that our family could live happily.)

8
00:00:43,359 --> 00:00:46,320
(Memorial tablet of late husband, Mr. Chun)
(But God did not grant my wish, my father...)

9
00:00:51,679 --> 00:00:54,399
Chun Jinrong, are you deaf?
What time is it now?

10
00:00:54,399 --> 00:00:55,456
Hurry up!

11
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:58,234
(Du Ruyu, 47)
(This is my mother who lives in anxiety)

12
00:00:58,234 --> 00:01:00,360
(Skilled in household management)
(about marrying her daughters.)

13
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,920
Mother, when we get there,

14
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:05,480
you must not shout and yell like this.

15
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:09,640
Besides, why are you in such a hurry?

16
00:01:10,359 --> 00:01:11,359
You're not in a hurry now?

17
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:13,079
You're already thirty. Do you know that?

18
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:15,319
Twenty-nine.

19
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:19,079
What's more,
you're not just waiting for me.

20
00:01:19,159 --> 00:01:21,760
I wonder
if Peilan's pastries are ready yet.

21
00:01:22,599 --> 00:01:24,920
Peilan, are the pastries ready yet?

22
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:27,296
(Chun Jinrong, 30)
(This is my eldest sister)

23
00:01:27,296 --> 00:01:29,300
(Versatile, with high aspiration)
(who wants to marry into a rich family.)

24
00:01:29,300 --> 00:01:30,740
(She's determined to
be a person above others.)

25
00:01:33,519 --> 00:01:36,719
On my way. Jinrong, here.

26
00:01:36,719 --> 00:01:38,640
It's still hot.
Taking it now is just right in time.

27
00:01:39,319 --> 00:01:40,799
Mother, when we get there,

28
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:42,079
just say that I made this.

29
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,120
Don't make mistakes.

30
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:46,040
Keep pretending. After you're married,
see how you keep doing so.

31
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,599
Hurry up and go.

32
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,480
(Although they occasionally quarrel,)

33
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:53,879
(I know they are the ones who care the most
for each other deep in their hearts.)

34
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:04,560
Why is my medicine less?

35
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,879
Is this medicine? Isn't this sugar?

36
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:09,536
It's poisonous.

37
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:21,039
(Chun Keling, 18, helps the weak,)
(This is my fourth sister. You'll never know)

38
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:23,159
(but gets beaten a lot)
(what kind of trouble she'll get into.)

39
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,599
This is a match made in heaven.

40
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,639
We haven't known each other for long,

41
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:32,479
but my son is particularly

42
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,439
satisfied with Jinrong.

43
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,560
What a fate.

44
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:40,319
Who would have thought
that Jinrong's fate

45
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,960
would be actually here?

46
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:43,759
Totally right.

47
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:49,039
If you had moved to Jianglin earlier,

48
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:52,400
maybe, we would
already have grandchildren.

49
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,240
It's not too late now.

50
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,400
It's not too late now.

51
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:59,080
Yeah, let's set the wedding date
on the seventh day of next month.

52
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:00,759
Let's settle this.

53
00:03:01,599 --> 00:03:02,560
Inedible.

54
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,680
(Jinrong is really virtuous.)

55
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:07,520
(Look at these pastries.
How good they look.)

56
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:09,000
(Have a taste.)

57
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,360
(Taste it.)

58
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,240
(It smells delicious.)

59
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,240
Don't eat it.

60
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,808
What are you doing?

61
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,240
Luckily, you didn't eat it.

62
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:34,719
Son, Son.

63
