♪Really extraordinary♪

66
00:04:07,972 --> 00:04:11,332
♪The cutie in the mirror♪

67
00:04:11,332 --> 00:04:14,436
♪Oh, looking a bit arrogant♪

68
00:04:14,436 --> 00:04:17,476
♪Every day, I sleep in and feel drowsy♪

69
00:04:17,476 --> 00:04:20,164
♪Sleepy and hungry.
Whose alarm clock got hit♪

70
00:04:20,164 --> 00:04:23,556
♪Only the body is lazy,
the spirit is very nice♪

71
